com.sri.ai.expresso.api

Interface CountingFormula

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable<java.lang.Object>, Expression, QuantifiedExpression, QuantifiedExpressionWithABody, java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultCountingFormula

    @Beta
public interface CountingFormula
extends QuantifiedExpressionWithABody
    An Expression that represents a counting formula, for example:
     | X in 1..10 : X < 5 |
 
 which are equivalent to the much more awkward and redundant 
 
 | {{ (on X in 1..10) X | X < 5 }} |
    which have the express goal of representing a number of satisfying solutions.
    Author:
    braz
